    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation results confirm CFD model predicts hemolysis index within acceptable error bounds across all five CPB operating points. RH < 1 criterion satisfied for worst-case condition. Model is credible for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
